name: Ember Ushi! Milk Bounce
description:
You're a big tiddie cowgirl in some seedy bar. There's only one thing to do. Bounce various milk containers on your boobs

Obviously.

Bounce milk, collect power ups, score points.

Controls are simple.

A or Left Arrow - Move Left

D or Right Arrow - Move Right

Space or Up Arrow - Jump

This game requires Java to work. If the game does not launch you may not have Java installed.  Download Java Here -> https://www.java.com/

While only a windows EXE is provided, the game should run perfectly on Linux through WINE.
